divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking pictures of an eagle in the air on a side road. I did not see the object until I downloaded my pictures and my jaw hit the ground because I knew I had caught something on camera. I was so excited and went around showing every one at work couldnt beleave the picture. Now every time I go by that spot I stop and take alot of pictures.
